-MAIN
 Here you have a general look on the station.
                                                          
-STARPORT
 On our landing-field are several ships which bring you to all the good 
 destinations in the galaxy. Also you can check the actual space-weather
 before you start your trip.
 -DISCOVERY
  Explore the universe and the Blue Planet. With the included timemachine you can
  also travel back in time.
 -BATTLESTAR GALACTICA
  Various destinations in the science fiction-universe.
 -MILLENNIUM FALCON
  Han Solo and Chewbacca bring you into the Star Wars-Galaxy.  
 -USS STARGAZER
  Here you get into Star Trek.
 -UFO
  Travel with an UFO. Find out the truth about Aliens and their visits on Earth.
 -WHITE STAR
  Your ship to bring you into Babylon5.

-APARTMENTS
